{"source":"linkedin","source_id":"4407470903","title":"Sales Manager","company":"Qureos","location":"Dubai","remote":true,"salary":"","posted_at":"","url":"https://easyapply.jobs/r/zGDoEHz26m9CDz2E8Gfn","description":"Job Overview\n\nQureos is revolutionising the way young people learn and work by offering job matching, one-on-one mentorships, and hands-on projects across in-demand fields. We are seeking a dynamic and results-driven Sales Manager to lead our sales efforts and drive business growth. This is a Full-Time position based in our Dubai, United Arab Emirates office. The ideal candidate will be a strategic thinker with a proven track record in sales leadership, capable of building and nurturing a high-performing team. You will be instrumental in expanding our client base and strengthening our market position, contributing directly to our mission of empowering the next generation of professionals.\n\nResponsibilities\n\n Develop and execute strategic sales plans to achieve sales targets and expand our customer base. Lead, mentor, and manage the sales team, fostering a culture of success and ongoing business goal achievement. Build and maintain strong, long-lasting relationships with key clients, stakeholders, and partners. Identify emerging markets and market shifts while being fully aware of new products and competition status. Manage the end-to-end sales cycle, from lead generation to closing deals, ensuring a seamless client experience. Provide accurate sales forecasts, reports, and analysis to senior management. Collaborate with the marketing and product teams to align strategies and enhance sales opportunities. Represent Qureos at industry events, conferences, and networking functions to promote our brand and solutions.\n\nQualifications\n\n Proven experience as a Sales Manager or in a similar senior sales role, with a demonstrable track record of success. Excellent communication, negotiation, and presentation skills. Strong leadership qualities with the