ropositions to senior level executives.Prospect, forecast, resource allocation, and planning of new business deals.Forecast sales activity and revenue achievement in CRM tool, while creating and maintaining satisfied customers.Achieve quarterly sales objectives and forecast sales activity accurately\nWhat You’ll Need:Years of Experience required: 5-13 years.Sales Professionals with experience in SAAS and AI5 to 10 years of experience in software solution sales.Contract Management or Procurement or Supply Chain domain knowledge – must be able to have credible business conversations with procurement, legal and finance executives.Demonstrable track record of consistent over achievement of quotas and revenue goalsExperience in managing complex sales-cycles and demonstrated ownership of territory and account management.Outstanding communication (written and oral), negotiation, presentation and solution selling skills to manage complex organizations.Demonstrated ability to work in an environment where growth and change is the only constant.Proficiency in Microsoft Word, PowerPoint, ExcelArabic Speaking is mandatoryA bachelor’s degree from a reputable institution\nCommitment to Diversity and Inclusion: We are an equal opportunity employer committed to diversity and inclusion. We do not discriminate based on race, color, gender, religion, national origin, ancestry, age, disability, medical condition, genetic information, military or veteran status, marital status, pregnancy, gender identity, sexual orientation, or any other protected characteristic. We provide reasonable accommodations for disabled employees and applicants as required by law. These principles apply to all aspects of employment, including recruitment, training, promotions, compensation, benefits, transfers, and social programs."}
