out volume + quality + speed.\n\nRequirements\nBackground in ecommerce, recruiting, staffing, or appointment setting (preferred)\nComfortable doing daily outreach and handling lots of conversations\nStrong written English - you’ll message candidates all day\nOrganized, proactive, and reliable\nUsed to tracking leads and following systems\nComfortable with CRM tools (Airtable / ClickUp experience is a plus)\nCan move fast without losing accuracy\nConfident holding warm, natural conversations\nOwnership mindset - you don’t wait to be told\nBenefits\nWork directly with fast-scaling DTC brands worldwide\nLearn modern recruiting + high-performance outreach systems\nFully remote with structured routines and clear expectations\nNo chaos, no guessing - clean systems and transparent KPIs\nDirect access to leadership\nGrowth path into Interview Manager or Client Manager roles"}
